OL,5, A senior HSBC executive who accused    
OL,6, central bankers and officials of       
OL,7, exaggerating the financial risks of    
OL,8, climate change has resigned.           
OL,10,FStuart Kirk, the bank's global head of 
OL,11,Fresponsible investing, was reportedly  
OL,12,Fsuspended in May after he said in a    
OL,13,Fspeech: "There's always some nut job   
OL,14,Ftelling me about the end of the world."
OL,16,FHe said on Thursday his comments had   
OL,17,Fmade his position "unsustainable".     
OL,19,F"A cancel culture destroys wealth and  
OL,20,Fprogress," he added in a LinkedIn post.
